Patience, I know I could always use more, how about you? Sometimes all we need is a reminder.. Gardening is a fun hobby that enhances family time, brings in deep respect for nature and teaches patience. 
But before you dive into a large project, begin with a small "Magic Garden".🌱
.
What you'll need?
Planter or pot, Dirt, Flowers, Rocks, Birdhouse, Planting tools.🌻
.
Step 1: Fill the Planter or Pot With Dirt
Use planting tools to root flower buds or seeds into the soil. Arrange rocks and birdhouse on top to design your own landscape.
.
Step 2: Sprinkle With "Fairy Dust"
Shh, our "fairy dust" is just glitter but it's still magical. Sprinkle some over and wait for make-believe fairies to come out to play! 💫
.
